Ing '''Sorsogon State College (SSC)''', ing sadiang Sorsogon College of Arts and Trades (SCAT), ing metung kareng pekamatuang [[w:trade school|trade school]] king [[Filipinas]]. Mitátag ya antimong Sorsogon Trade School kanitang [[1907]], Kaibat ning walumpulu’t anam (86) a banua, megi yang metung a kolehiyung pang-estadu (state college) kapamilata’ning Leyi ning Republica (Republic Act) No. 
7666, a inapruban nang Presidenti Fidel V. Ramos. Mayayakit ya ing Kolehiyu king Dalang Magsaysay, [[Sorsogon Lakanbalen]] (Magsaysay Street, Sorsogon City).    

